tilemap-studio (4.0.1-1foundry1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial Foundry Linux packaging of Tilemap Studio (v4.0.1).
  * Statically links vendored FLTK 1.4.5, built X11-only
    (FLTK_BACKEND_WAYLAND=0), per upstream's supported build; Ubuntu 26.04
    ships FLTK 1.4.4 as a Wayland-hybrid build that the upstream X11
    transparency code will not compile against.

